               <msContents>
                  <summary>Photocopy of excerpts from mss: Abb(adie) 28, Minor Prophets, excerpt from Judges with commentary, Hosea, Amos, Micah, Joel, Obadiah, Jonah, Nahum, Habakkuk, Zephaniah, Haggai, Zechariah, Malachi,  Treatise on Melki Zedek; Abbadie 126: Excerpts from Commentary on Orit, Genesis, Exodus, Leviticus, Numbers, Deuteronomy, Joshua; Abbadie 156: Commentary of John Crysostom on Orit, (Genesis, Exodus, </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1v" to="26r" facs="002">Fols 1v–26r</locus><title>Abb(adie) 156</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpts from Abb(adie) 156 (dated seventeenth / eighteenth century), Minor Prophets, excerpt from Judges with commentary, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3144Hosea">Za-Hoseʿ
                                                  nabiyy</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3145Amos">Za-ʾAmoṣ nabiyy</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3146Micah">Za-Mikyās
                                                  nabiyy</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1689Joel">Book of Joel</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3147Obadiah">ዘአብድዩ፡ ነቢይ።</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1694Jonah">Book of Jonah</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2057Bookof">Book of Nahum</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1567Bookof">Book of
                                                  Habakkuk</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3148Zephan">Za-Sofonyās
                                                  nabiyy</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3149Haggai">Za-Ḥagge
                                                  nabiyy</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3150Zechar">Za-Zakāryās
                                                  nabiyy</title>, <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3151Malachi">Za-Milkǝyās
                                                  nabiyy</title>, excerpt from a work dealing with the names and locations of the prophets, incomplete at the end (<locus target="#25v">fols. 25v, </locus>), Treatise on Melki Zedek (<locus target="#26r">fol. 26r</locus>)</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="26v" to="44v" facs="027">Fols 26v–44v</locus><title>Abbadie 156</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpts from Abbadie 156 (dated seventeenth / eighteenth century): Excerpts from Commentary of John Crysostom on Orit, Genesis, Exodus, Leviticus, Numbers, Deuteronomy, Joshua; Judges, Ruth</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="45v" to="132r" facs="046">Fols 45v–132r</locus><title>Abbadie 28</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpts from Abbadie 28 (dated as seventeenth or eighteenth century): Commentary of John Crystostom on Orit Genesis (<locus target="#45r">fols. 45r, </locus>), Exodus (<locus target="#82r">82r, </locus>), Leviticus (<locus target="#98r">98r, </locus>), Numbers (<locus target="#108v">108v, </locus>), Deuteronomy (<locus target="#119r">119r, </locus>), Joshua (<locus target="#128r">128r</locus>), incomplete at the end, Excerpt from the chronicles of Wänag Sägǝd [the throne name of Lǝbnä Dǝngǝl]</note>
                </msItem>
               </msContents>
